name: Alyssa Sutherland LoRA
description:
This is my first Lora uploaded here, it is trained on 48 images from Alyssa Sutherland at 2100 steps using Kohya, it produces nice images using photo realistic models such as: Love Journey, Lofi, Protogen and Clarity.

Feel free to test it and suggest other models that can handle it well.

Recommended weight is .6 -.9
